      "writtenOn": "2026-07-17T07:20:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e I don\u0027t think requeuing strategies belong to this change, but rather to 529865773.\n\u003e \n\u003e https://issues.gerritcodereview.com/issues/529865773\n\nYou can find another strategy for retrying, of course, but you can\u0027t leave this change without that logic implemented.\n\nIf requeuing isn\u0027t an option, you\u0027d need to find another option.",
